<HEADLINE>
MOVIE TICKET PRICE HITS $8.50
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAVE McNARY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES -- The $10 movie ticket looks more and more
inevitable.
</P>
<P>
   On Friday, AMC became the first chain in Los Angeles to reach
