<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-10 03:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3083 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-LAKERS-REWRITE-LA     04-10 0640
