<DOCNO> NYT19990410.0057 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-10 10:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5116 &Cx1f; var-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-GENOCIDE-REVIE     04-10 0647
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-KOSOVO-GENOCIDE-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 UNDATED: general attention.  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The e-mail from Serbia is characterized by an overwhelming sense
