<HEADLINE>
MAKE MONEY WHILE YOU SLEEP! IN YOUR DREAMS. 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact Olivia Vasquez in Los
Angeles (Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089)  
 (bl)  
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Get-rich-quick schemes have been around a long time. But with
the rise of home businesses in this era of prosperity, magazines
for small-scale entrepreneurs are fairly bursting lately with
come-ons to put you on Easy Street.
</P>
<P>
   Uncle Sam got you in the poor house with the April 15 tax
deadline approaching? Unable to claim that nifty home office
deduction? The ads excerpted below may or may not help.
</P>
<P>
   _ By JOE SHARKEY
</P>
<P>
   .............................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 1 _ Business is HOT, I tell you:
</P>
<P>
   FIREFIGHTERS WANTED
</P>
<P>
   Will Pay $1 Million Dollars
</P>
<P>
   You're driving down the road. You see a house on fire, and you
think, ``I hope to God nobody is inside.'' You arrive to see the
homeowner in shock. The wife and the kids are hysterical and the
dog is missing. Everything they own is gone. Do you think, at this
point, the homeowners would pay you $1,500 to stop the fire and put
everything back the way it was before it started? Of course they
would! They'd probably pay you 100 times that. ... Making big
money, saving lives and preventing a family's home from disaster.
There's not a more honorable business available on earth!
</P>
<P>
   _ In the April Entrepreneur magazine, hawking dealerships for a
flame-retardant spray.
</P>
<P>
   ....................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 2 _ Hey, maybe that basket-weaving elective I took in
college is finally paying off:
</P>
<P>
   Own Your Own Home Basket Business
</P>
<P>
   Join other successful women in making money with your own home
basket business. ... Complete start-up including basket inventory
is $1,250.
</P>
<P>
   _ Start Your Own Business magazine, summer 1999.
</P>
<P>
   .....................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 3 _ The fedora is extra, pal:
</P>
<P>
   Be a DETECTIVE
</P>
<P>
   Explore a secret world! Experience a new adventure every day.
Fascinating new career. Dynamic home-study course. Diploma, badge.
</P>
<P>
   _ Start Your Own Business
</P>
<P>
   ........................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 4 _ Help me get this soggy dollar into that slot, will
ya?:
</P>
<P>
   Make Money on Millions of Drinkers
</P>
<P>
   Unique life-saving machine that accepts coins or dollar bills.
This machine can be placed in bars, discos, nightclubs or any place
alcohol is served. ... Its turbo-electronic circuitry determines
breath alcohol levels in five seconds. Why does our machine make a
lot of money? IT TALKS! Our machine gives 27 different responses in
a female voice, with a large three-digit readout. This is a product
whose time has come.
</P>
<P>
   _ Entrepreneur, April
</P>
<P>
   Examples of the responses from the aforementioned, $1,695
``Coin-Operated Talking Breath Alcohol Analyzer,'' according to the
distributor's Web site (www.aaanalyzers.com):
</P>
<P>
   _ You are OK ...
</P>
<P>
   _ You are High. Slow down. ...
</P>
<P>
   _ You are BOMBED. Call a taxi! ...
</P>
<P>
   _ Do not try to get lucky tonight! ...
</P>
<P>
   ...........................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 5 _ Honey, can you give me a hand with this blimp?:
</P>
<P>
   Skyview Aerial Photo introduces you to the BLIMP-CAM!
</P>
<P>
   Our miniature tethered BLIMP CAM system takes aerial photos and
videos using digital remote up to 500 feet. ... Excellent home
business ... International dealerships available. ...
</P>
<P>
   _ Entrepreneur, April
</P>
<P>
   .............................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 6 _ And they call it the ``idiot box'':
</P>
<P>
   Like me, you can make really BIG MONEY at home watching TV. . .
. I live the really good life in a fabulous secluded ``paradise''
miles away from the city crowds and traffic. ... I'll show you. ...
Most people just watch the news _ I use it to make large profits.
... Remember the last big freeze in Florida? I used the news to
turn a few hundred dollars into $19,919 in just seven weeks!
</P>
<P>
   _ May issue of Small Business Opportunities magazine.
</P>
<P>
   .............................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 7 _ Do I really have to talk to you?:
</P>
<P>
   Here it is! The ultimate work-at-home Money Making Opportunity.
Earn $2,500.00 per day without talking to anyone (except me!) ...
Unlike other ``hit and run'' companies that sell you money-making
programs and then leave you high and dry, I'll be here to assist
you personally when you need help. I've helped hundreds of people
just like you make lots of money, and now it's your turn. I'll even
include my personal phone number with the program.
</P>
<P>
   _ Small Business Opportunities
</P>
<P>
   ................................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 8 _ I don't get out much anyway:
</P>
<P>
   MAKE $500 A DAY!
</P>
<P>
   When you receive my $500 a day system in the mail, I will give
you the special letter and I'll even tell you who to mail it to.
This is no trick or scam. ... You just mail out the letter I give
you and you receive a check for up to $500. ... NOT a chain letter,
NOT a pyramid scheme ... NOT a scam, con or trick, NOT making
telephone calls, NOT meeting anyone. ...
</P>
<P>
   _ Small Business Opportunities
</P>
<P>
   ..............................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 9 _ Could you breathe into the machine, please?:
</P>
<P>
   USE ME AND GET RICH!
</P>
<P>
   I am the originator of the most popular money-making plan in
existence today. Perhaps you've seen me on TV. I travel the country
telling people just like you how to cash in on the HUNDREDS OF
MILLIONS OF DOLLARS that magazines give away to anyone who follows
the simple directions that I have prepared. ...
</P>
<P>
   I stumbled on this wealth secret quite by accident. I was having
lunch with a friend who I hadn't seen in over three years. I
noticed her new diamond ring, new Mercedes and her $500 dress. At
first she kept quiet about it. But after two or three glasses of
wine, her face lit up and she began to talk. She told me one of the
most incredible secrets I have ever heard. She explained how she
got her new diamond ring, her new Mercedes and how she and her
husband are quietly banking over $40,000 per month in each of three
bank accounts.
</P>
<P>
   _ Small Business Opportunities
</P>
<P>
   .........................
</P>
<P>
   Ad No. 10 _ Sleeping on the job? No problem, man:
</P>
<P>
   You can make $700 to $2,500 a day BEFORE getting out of bed. ...
29-year-old Ex-Warehouse Laborer Reveals His Personal Blueprints on
an easy home-based business that took him from a series of broke,
dead-end jobs and unemployment to the creation of a nationwide
financial empire virtually overnight! ... In this business, you
make money while: sleeping in bed, taking a shower, sitting at your
pool, sitting on the couch watching TV. ... Buy your wife or
girlfriend a diamond ring!
</P>
<P>
   _ Small Business Opportunities
</P>
