<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-10 11:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3127 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  AM-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      04-10 1744
